<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Anmerkung des Editors</strong></h3>



<p>Willst du mehr Popup-Beispiele? Erhalte sofortigen Zugang zu mehr als 100 erprobten und getesteten Popup-Vorlagen (kostenlos).</p>



<p><a href="https://sleeknote.com/popup-examples">Durchstöbere unsere Popup-Galerie.</a></p>
</div></div>



<p>Es ist clever. Ein Besucher, der Matratzengrößen vergleicht, ist wahrscheinlich weiter auf der Reise des Käufers als jemand, der nach Schlafhilfen sucht. Also bittet Casper um eine E-Mail, statt um Feedback, und stellt seine Produkte in seinen Onboarding-E-Mails vor (mehr dazu in Teil 5).</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Aktion Gegenstand</strong>: Wenn du verschiedene Arten von Produkten verkaufst (z.B. Kosmetika wie Foundation), erstelle eine Vergleichsanleitung, die den Käufern hilft, das Richtige für sie zu finden. Bonus, wenn du es gut in den SERPs einordnen kannst.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="5"><strong>Strategie #5: Alle Rezensionen an einem Ort präsentieren (BoFu)</strong></h2>



<p>Du weißt, wie wichtig es ist, Kundenaussagen zu nutzen, um potenzielle Käufer zu gewinnen. Aber bringst du sie so gut wie möglich zur Geltung?</p>



<p>Da Casper weiß, wie wichtig Rezensionen in einem wettbewerbsintensiven Markt sind, stellt Casper alle seine Rezensionen auf einer Seite auf seiner Website aus.</p>



<p>Zuerst zeigen sie schriftliche Bewertungen ihrer Kunden, einschließlich des Namens der Person, woher sie kommen und wie sie Casper bewerten.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="532" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-1024x532.png" alt="19 Casper_s Reviews" class="wp-image-113814" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-1024x532.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-300x156.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-768x399.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-380x198.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-600x312.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-760x395.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-67x35.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-96x50.png 96w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-740x385.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-220x114.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-385x200.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews.png 1250w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>(Casper ist hier zu 100% transparent. Wenn du auf &#8222;Alle Bewertungen ansehen&#8220; klickst, kannst du alles lesen, was ihre Kunden über sie sagen, auch die unzufriedenen).</p>



<p>Unter ihren Kundenbewertungen kannst du Tweets von Kunden lesen, was die Legitimität ihrer Bewertungen weiter erhöht.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="393" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-1024x393.png" alt="20 Casper Tweet Testimonial" class="wp-image-113818" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-1024x393.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-300x115.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-768x294.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-380x146.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-600x230.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-760x291.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-91x35.png 91w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-130x50.png 130w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-740x284.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-220x84.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-385x148.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Schließlich fügt Casper noch die dritte Schicht der sozialen Beweise hinzu: Medienausweise und Erwähnungen in der Presse.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="646" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-1024x646.png" alt="21 Casper_s Media Mentions" class="wp-image-113822" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-1024x646.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-300x189.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-768x485.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-1536x969.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-380x240.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-600x379.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-760x479.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-1440x909.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-55x35.png 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-79x50.png 79w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-740x467.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-220x139.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-385x243.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions.png 1585w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Es gibt einen Grund, warum Casper sich so viel Mühe gibt, ihre Reviewseite zu optimieren, und wir werden in Teil 5: Strategie #2 besprechen, warum.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Aktion Gegenstand</strong>: Es ist üblich, dass Online-Shops ihre Rezensionen auf Seiten Dritter haben. Aber das bedeutet nicht immer, dass es sich dabei um die beste Praxis handelt. Nimm deine besten Rezensionen und veröffentliche sie auf einer Seite auf deiner Website, damit du mehr Kontrolle darüber hast, wie du dein Geschäft vermarktest.&nbsp;</p>
</div></div>



<h2><strong>Teil 3: Linkaufbau</strong></h2>



<p>Zum Zeitpunkt des Schreibens hat Casper 148k Backlinks von 5.54 verweisenden Domains.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="152" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-1024x152.png" alt="22 Casper_s Backlinks" class="wp-image-113826" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-1024x152.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-300x44.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-768x114.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-1536x227.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-380x56.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-600x89.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-760x113.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-1440x213.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-180x27.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-250x37.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-740x110.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-220x33.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-385x57.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Es ist beeindruckend, aber solange man kein Multi-Millionen-Dollar Marketingbudget hat, sind nur wenige ihrer Linkbuilding-Strategien replizierbar (wenn du neugierig bist, habe ich meine drei Favoriten in die Bonusressource aufgenommen).</p>



<p>Anstatt also das Unreplizierbare zu erforschen, möchte ich euch drei unkonventionelle Wege zeigen, wie Casper Links baut und wie ihr das auch könnt.&nbsp;</p>



<h2 id="6"><strong>Strategie #6: White-Hat Education Links bauen mit &#8222;Die CSD-Methode&#8220;.</strong></h2>



<p>Wenn du etwas über Linkaufbau weißt, weißt du, dass .edu-Links das Beste sind, was du bekommen kannst. Sie haben eine MASSE an Page Rank, aber sie sind auch schwer zu bekommen. Es sei denn, natürlich, du hast einen einzigartigen Blickwinkel&#8230;</p>



<p>Wirf einen Blick auf Caspers referring Domains.</p>



<p>Wenn wir die Suche verfeinern, können wir sehen, dass sie zwölf do-follow .edu-Links gebaut haben, die, wie ich es nenne, die College Student Discount (CSD)-Strategie verwenden.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="536" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-1024x536.png" alt="23 Education Links to Casper" class="wp-image-113830" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-1024x536.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-300x157.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-768x402.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-1536x804.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-380x199.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-600x314.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-760x398.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-1440x754.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-67x35.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-95x50.png 95w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-740x388.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-220x115.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-385x202.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Also, was macht Casper, um diese Links zu bauen?&nbsp;</p>



<p>Sie fügen ihr Produkt in das Leben eines Marktes ein, der davon profitieren könnte:</p>



<p><em>Die Studenten.</em></p>



<p>Schau dir diese Seite von der California State University, Northridge (CSUN) an:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-1024x640.png" alt="24 Link from CSUN" class="wp-image-113834" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Link-from-CSUN.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Auf ihr können Studenten Rabatte für eine Reihe von Produkten und Dienstleistungen erhalten, darunter Kleidung, Versicherungen und Matratzen.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="149" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-1024x149.png" alt="25 Casper Discount Code" class="wp-image-113838" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-1024x149.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-300x44.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-768x112.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-1536x223.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-380x55.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-600x87.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-760x111.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-1440x209.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-180x26.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-250x36.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-740x108.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-220x32.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code-385x56.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Casper-Discount-Code.png 1650w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Zufall? Vielleicht. Aber wahrscheinlich nicht.</p>



<p>Hier ist noch ein Beispiel von der State University of New York, wieder mit einer Seite über Rabatte bei Produkten und Dienstleistungen für Studenten.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-1024x640.png" alt="26 Link from SUNY" class="wp-image-113842" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Wenn du nach unten scrollst, haben auch sie einen Rabatt auf jede Casper-Matratze.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="274" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-1024x274.png" alt="27 Casper Discount Code 2" class="wp-image-113846" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-1024x274.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-300x80.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-768x205.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-1536x410.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-380x102.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-600x160.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-760x203.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-1440x385.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-131x35.png 131w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-187x50.png 187w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-740x198.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-220x59.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-385x103.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/20